@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nlsizf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.02) + 0.25) - ((v2 + 0.01 * v1 + 0.37) - (v1 + 0.07 - v0 + 0.36)))
    v1 = wp.abs(0.78)
    tmp = wp.abs((v1 - (v0 + 0.92 + v0 + 0.72)))
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.82 * v2 + 0.34)) - (wp.exp(v2 + 0.60) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.70)))
    v0 = ((tmp / (tmp + 0.82 + v0 + 0.04)) + wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.20)))
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
